### Modifications

Exclude jackson transitive dependencies from swagger-io.

**Note:**  this PR is created on top of #2128 so, I will rebase it once, #2128 is merged.

### Motivation

In #2128 , Function-worker updates metrics periodically so, we can fetch function-metrics on demand. Now, we would like to keep function-metrics as part of functions stats so, we can get it on demand and build monitoring on it, same as like we can get for pulsar topics: `pulsar-admin persistent stats-internal <topic>`

### Modifications

expose function-metrics using admin-api call.

### Result

